normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有好多父母都要由朝返到夜晚十一二點先返 最多俾錢小朋友自己理掂自己 邊有時間管教吖陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以真係好睇你識啲咩朋友"},{"pid":"ebe2896e312983bd53c60c3411629f89f34b8a18","tid":460551,"uid":9284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"想打鳩佢地"},{"pid":"d587144f02d57b9f5cd79a2be89b10cf1796e3ff","tid":460551,"uid":120801,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T20:32:30.000Z","msg":"出發點好 但佢地老母都管唔到<br />\n外人又可以點<br />\n<br />\n青春期就係咁反叛 睇大D會唔會醒<br />\n同埋唔好做D野係大個唔可以修補到<br />\n好似大肚 踏出校 吸毒 入女童等"},{"pid":"2290caa71cae0ee72e1d6682d796d99b63a6c3de","tid":460551,"uid":119399,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T00:53:24.000Z","msg":"所以話住既地方好重要&hellip;成日話公屋無問題果啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bb3a44182dd1e04b119bc7c07d216685e9897a","tid":460551,"uid":18309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"扺啦"},{"pid":"07d24939882a50f4781155f9b9e0148e5a21e798","tid":460551,"uid":45941,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁撚細個食煙以為自己好撚型</blockquote><br />\n所以其實真係好憎人食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食煙係個人意願冇所謂，但真係希望啲人會企定一個位食，將影響減到最低"},{"pid":"0e2394a1c5e75b0c04c4d02157832bdea211aac9","tid":460551,"uid":28002,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"無人會覺得自己MK<br />\n果啲mk仔，妹睇完你篇野依舊會繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804b5cebaeecb5ce3f947bc63c187e7aaeb09249","tid":460551,"uid":136576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有名你叫MK仔，識諗就唔會群埋班MK仔玩啦</blockquote><br />\n呢個歲數有邊個會識諗？唔係屋企人管住係好易群埋mk度<br />\n屋企人唔識教唔識管先係最大問題囉<img 